    While exploring a large maze of underground tunnels in the state of
        Nevada, USA. You emerge near the entrance to a 'TOP SECRET'        
     Military installation. Cautiously, you decide to sneak around and
        explore the area. While nearing a large building, gun shots, 
        screams and other sounds are heard. Around the corner of the 
    building, a man comes stumbling towards you, and falls at your feet.
    The man appears badly injured, but he manages to tell you a horrible
    story....

            'Inside the large building a group of scientist's and
             I, have been working on a project called 'CY-CLONE'.
             'CY-CLONE', involved taking DNA from some soldiers
             and combining it with a Super Computers artifical
             intelligence. 
             Then using an altered radioactive isotope, along with
             cloning, we were able to create a race of beings called
             Cyborgs.
             The purpose of our project, was to create a race of 
             warriors for a possible future engagement between 
             humans and an extraterrestial race.
             Unfortunately, the Super Computer used to give the 
             Cyborgs, their artificial intelligence, was infected
             with a virus. The virus caused the Cyborgs to change,
             they soon regarded anyone or anything other than
             themselves, as extraterrestials.
              
             Every human inside is dead, and I am slowly dying...
            
             You must stop the Cyborgs! If they are not stopped
             they will soon start cloning themselves and take over
             the world.

             Follow me....

            
    
    Limping badly, the scientist manages to take you inside the lower
    level of the installation, to the main 'CY-CLONE Cloning Chamber'.
        As you enter a room a massive door slams shut behind you, 
    separating you from the scientist. You stand patiently on a gold
        colored platform. Suddenly, a strange beam of green light 
    envelops you. Your body feels like it's on fire. The pain grows
    more and more intense, then you hear the scientist talking to you
    over an intercom....


             'In a couple minutes you will faint, when you 
              become conscious again, you will be a Cyborg.
              There will be three of you! If all three of 
               yourselves are killed, the world is doomed. 
              If you destroy most of the Cyborgs and make    
             it through all six levels of the installation,
             the computer will change you back into a human           
             again.

             Good Luck!

            Oh yea... You will be armed with a phase-gun, it's
            good for three blasts, then you will have to locate
                another one. I don't think you will have any 
               problem finding another weapon when you need it, 
            just keep a look-out.
            Now let me tell you about the levels and the Cyborgs
            on each...

           
            
            LEVEL 1:
            --------
              This level contains the blue dummies, as we called
              them. They have no intelligence as of yet!
              Back and forth they go on a mindless quest of
              nothingness...
              These blue dummies reside on every level of the
              installation, along with the Cyborgs below...
              
            LEVEL 2:
            --------
              Here is where something strange has happened, the
              Cyborgs have created a Red warrior, we never did
              figure out what his purpose was, is he just 
              another dummy or is there more to him than meets
              the eye...Beware!
               
            LEVEL 3:
            --------
              Caution must be used here! The Cyborgs have nade
              their first armed warrior, this Dark Blue terror
              is on a rampage of destruction.

            LEVEL 4:
            --------
              This level contains a White Cyborg, but in this
              case, white doesn't represent good. This warrior
              has been given a small amount of artificial
              intelligence, he will try to track you down while
              firing a blast of phase energy at you.
              Even worse he is equipped with a energy absorbing
              shield. It will take one blast of your Phase-gun
              to neutralize the shield before he is vunerable.

            LEVEL 5:
            --------
              The Golden Boy lives here! That's what we use to
              call him. Beware, he's no boy.. This terror has 
              an even stronger shield then the White Cyborg.
              It will take two blasts of your Phase-gun to
              neutralize the shield before he is vunerable.
              Watch out, he is even more smarter and aggressive
              than the White Cyborg.
           
            LEVEL 6:
            --------
              This is Terror! The Golden Cyborgs have created
              a new warrior. He is fast, and glides along
              silently. It is unknown if he has a weapon,
              but one thing we know for sure is he has an
              intelligence greater than any other Cyborg.
              He has the shield power of the golden cyborgs
              plus one feature no other Cyborg has.
              He is invisible.....
             
