                      ***>>>  HOW TO PLAY  <<***
                      
  When you arrive on a level, you are the green cyborg. Immediately move
  to a partial safe area. What is a partial safe area, you ask? Any place
  away from the corners of the screen. In the corners you will see flashing
  spots of energy, these are Cyborg teleport pods, where you see a pod, a
  Cyborg will soon appear.
  Use a joystick to move your Cyborg...
  Pressing the fire button shoots a blast from your Phase-gun in the
  direction you are facing, unless your out of ammo, in this case locate
  and pick up another gun, by touching it.
  At the top of the screen is the 'SCORE:' the score increases by 
  destroying Cyborgs. Cyborgs have different point or score values, so you
  can clear a level faster by destroying the cyborgs that are worth more.
  Of course the Cyborgs that are worth more, are also the most dangerous.
  LIVES: is the number of Cyborgs or lives you have remaining, if it says
  2, that means one in reserve and the one your now controlling, etc..

  Here are the score-points needed to complete each level and the score-
  points that the different colored Cyborgs are worth:
      
      LEVEL 1: Blue Dummies 100
               3000 points needed to advance ot level 2
       
      LEVEL 2: Red Dummies 300
               6000 points needed to advance to level 3

      LEVEL 3: Dark Blue 300
               12000 points needed to advance to level 4

      LEVEL 4: White 400
               19000 points needed to advance to level 5
       
      LEVEL 5: Golden 400
               29000 points needed to advance to level 6

      LEVEL 6: Invisible 600
               39000 points needed to win the game...
