                             - TECHNICAL-

          This game was written on my AMIGA 1200 68020 system,
          which has 2 megs of chip ram, and 8 megs of fast ram.

          It can be played on an AMIGA 500-600 system, but is
          about 3 times slower. How do I know this? Because I
            have an AMIGA 600 with 2 megs of chip ram only.

            
        It is written in AMOS. The only amal code is the routine
        to control the player and his weapon blast. The enemy 
        Cyborgs and their weapon blasts, etc. are all in regular
        or non-amal code. This uses all native 'AMOS THE CREATOR'
        commands, no extensions such as TOME, etc. 
        Everything is BOBS no sprites are used...
        It was created in two months, working at a calm pace...
